[{"_1":2},"llms/mdx",{"_3":4},"data","# Installation (/docs/installation)\n\n\n\nInstallation [#installation]\n\n`fwdx` has two sides:\n\n* a public server\n* one or more tunnel clients\n\nRequirements [#requirements]\n\n* Go `1.25+` to build from source\n* a Linux server with a public IP for the server side\n* a domain such as `tunnel.example.com`\n* TLS certificates for the public hostname\n\nPaths [#paths]\n\n* Server binary: `/usr/local/bin/fwdx`\n* Client config: `~/.fwdx/client.json`\n* Detached runtime state: `~/.fwdx/run`\n\nNext Steps [#next-steps]\n\n* [Install the server](/docs/installation/server)\n* [Install the client](/docs/installation/client)\n"]
